{"id":"bb38efb7-c952-4e85-a0f8-37f93d91a3b8","name":"Humanity refused to die - ZZZ - Zenless Zone Zero - RPG","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">What we fight for, is<strong> <u>New Eridu</u></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Zs9egzCXWIY7AfKwSo1Hr.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\">.</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\">.</span></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(159, 185, 255);\">◈─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 173, 251);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 151, 255);\">◈</span><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 100, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 225, 251);\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 100, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 138, 255);\"><strong>We</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 159, 255);\"><strong>lc</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 183, 255);\"><strong>om</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 212, 251);\"><strong>e t</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 225, 251);\"><strong>o N</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 212, 251);\"><strong>ew </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 183, 255);\"><strong>Ee</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 159, 255);\"><strong>ri</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 138, 255);\"><strong>du | </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 151, 255);\">◈</span><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 173, 251);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(159, 185, 255);\">─◈</span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 233, 251);\">The day the </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 248, 255);\"><strong>Hollows</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 233, 251);\"> came, humanity as we knew it was pushed to the </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 248, 255);\"><strong>brink of extinction</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 233, 251);\">. When the purple voids </span><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 217, 251);\">took hold, one could only speculate about how this would all end.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 212, 251);\">Yet, it was not the end.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 248, 255);\"><strong>New Eridu</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 183, 255);\"> rose from the ashes of </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 248, 255);\"><strong>Old Eridu</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(211, 183, 255);\">. Against every obstacle, the city endures, a living testament to humanity </span><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 159, 255);\">before the fall. It now serves as the <strong>Vanguard</strong> against the dangers of the Hollows, while the world outside lies in ruin. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 138, 255);\">Humanity's story is far from over.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 138, 255);\">And </span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 248, 255);\"><strong><u>YOU</u></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 138, 255);\"> are one of the few remaining who dares to walk what's left of Earth.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\">.</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\">.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4JotcC45EQjTO1k-GP-7h.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\">.</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\">.</span></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(159, 185, 255);\">◈─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 173, 251);\">─</span><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 151, 255);\">◈</span><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 100, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(212, 225, 251);\"><strong>|</strong></span><span style=\"color: